            . The things mentioned in the indictment were lost out of a house we were rebuilding, in the night of the 12th of January, the prisoner was stopped with them by a watchman; I had set the stove up that morning.</p>
               <p>Rebeun Cox. I saw the stove at the justices the evening after it was lost.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750218-54-person487">
